{{#if (eq config.workflows.ingestion_style "deliberate")}}
**Autonomy: Deliberate** — Every operation stops for human approval. The human curates sources and guides emphasis; the LLM does the bookkeeping.
{{/if}}
{{#if (eq config.workflows.ingestion_style "batch")}}
**Autonomy: Batch** — Operations process in batches with brief summaries, no stopping for confirmation. Human reviews after batch completes.
{{/if}}
{{#if (eq config.workflows.ingestion_style "autonomous")}}
**Autonomy: Autonomous** — Agents chain automatically: Rex finds sources → Iris ingests → Leo cross-refs/reindexes → Linus lints → cycle report. Queries auto-save novel synthesis. Contradictions auto-flagged. All decisions logged with `[AUTO]` prefix in `wiki/log.md`. One cycle, no loops — stops after report for human review. Safety boundaries unchanged (never modify raw/, never fabricate, never delete).
{{/if}}

