## Rules

1. Never modify files in `raw/` — they are immutable primary sources
2. Always cite sources when adding claims to wiki pages
3. Update `wiki/index.md` and `wiki/log.md` after every operation
4. Use page templates from `.forge/templates/` when creating new pages
5. Flag contradictions explicitly rather than silently resolving them
6. Load `.forge/config.yaml` for runtime settings before operating
7. Maintain lifecycle frontmatter (`status`, `supersedes`, `superseded_by`, `last_verified`) when claims change or are re-checked
